---
/**
 * MinorCaseStudies — BFCM hero cards + supporting case study grid + CTA
 * Extracted from CaseStudies.astro so /2 can use them independently.
 */

const cases = [
  {
    client: "OTAA",
    segment: "Accessories · 8-Figure Brand",
    before: "21%",
    after: "40%",
    metric: "Email contribution to revenue",
    timeframe: "90 days",
    quote:
      "e2 doubled our revenue growth to almost 40% and brought groundbreaking changes. His guidance during Black Friday led to the busiest week in our company's history.",
    author: "Fameez Haroon, Co-Founder",
  },
];
---

<section class="pt-24 pb-16 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-950 to-gray-950 pointer-events-none"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="section-container relative z-10">
    <!-- Section Headline -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-rose-400 mb-4">
        BFCM Results
      </p>
      <h2
        class="font-black text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight tracking-tight mb-5 text-balance"
      >
        The brands that print money on Black Friday are our clients.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        While everyone else guesses, our clients run BFCM like a machine. Here's
        the proof.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- BFCM Hero #1: Nail Cosmetics Brand -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-0 rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-2xl shadow-rose-500/5"
      >
        <div
          class="lg:w-[45%] bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-900 to-gray-950 p-10 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-between"
        >
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-rose-500/15 border border-rose-500/25 flex items-center justify-center text-rose-400 text-lg"
              >
                💅
              </div>
              <span
                class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-rose-400"
                >BFCM Email Strategy</span
              >
            </div>
            <h3
              class="font-black text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-none tracking-tight mb-4"
            >
              421% YoY BFCM<br />Email Revenue
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
              A Nail Cosmetics brand came to us after a flat BFCM season:
              diluted messaging, low volume, poor deliverability. We rebuilt
              everything and took them from A$200k to over A$1M in email revenue
              in a single BFCM period.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span class="text-rose-400">✓</span> 28 targeted campaigns with laser
                segmentation
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span class="text-rose-400">✓</span> Pre-BFCM deliverability warmup
                rebuilt inbox placement
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span class="text-rose-400">✓</span> Single unified sales message,
                zero dilution
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-10 text-xs text-gray-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide"
          >
            Anonymous · Nail Cosmetics · eCommerce
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="lg:w-[55%] bg-gray-950/50 border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-white/10 p-10 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-center"
        >
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-5">
            <div
              class="col-span-2 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6"
            >
              <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-1">
                <div class="text-xl font-black text-gray-600">A$200,732</div>
                <div class="text-gray-600">→</div>
                <div class="text-4xl font-black text-rose-400">A$1,045,096</div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide"
              >
                Email Revenue · BFCM Period
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-1">421%</div>
              <div
                class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
              >
                YoY Revenue Growth
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-1">48.5%↓</div>
              <div
                class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
              >
                Unsubscribe Rate
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="col-span-2 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5"
            >
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-1">A$3,748,975</div>
              <div
                class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
              >
                Total BFCM Revenue (Email Was the #1 Driver)
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-rose-500/5 border border-rose-500/20 p-5">
            <p class="text-sm text-rose-300/80 leading-relaxed italic">
              "A single launch email generated A$80,198. Black Friday is won
              before it starts. Deliverability, hype, and precision
              segmentation."
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-2 font-semibold">
              e2 Agency BFCM Case Study · Verified via Klaviyo
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BFCM Hero #2: Eyewear Brand (Email + SMS) -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse gap-0 rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-2xl shadow-indigo-500/5"
      >
        <div
          class="lg:w-[45%] bg-gradient-to-bl from-gray-900 via-gray-900 to-gray-950 p-10 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-between"
        >
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-500/15 border border-indigo-500/25 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-400 text-lg"
              >
                👓
              </div>
              <span
                class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-400"
                >Email + SMS BFCM Retention</span
              >
            </div>
            <h3
              class="font-black text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-none tracking-tight mb-4"
            >
              128% More Retention Revenue. One BFCM.
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
              A major Eyewear brand had plateaued at $1.5M email BFCM revenue.
              Solid strategy, but missing the 10% that adds millions. We rebuilt
              frequency, segmentation, timezone targeting, and SMS and unlocked
              $2.6M in new retention revenue.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span class="text-indigo-400">✓</span> Timezone-based segmentation
                across US, UK &amp; AU
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span class="text-indigo-400">✓</span> 29 targeted campaigns + omni-channel
                SMS hype
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span class="text-indigo-400">✓</span> Launch day alone: $1,284,826
                in revenue
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-10 text-xs text-gray-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide"
          >
            Anonymous · Eyewear · eCommerce
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="lg:w-[55%] bg-gray-950/50 border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-r border-white/10 p-10 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-center"
        >
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-5">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
              <div class="text-base font-black text-gray-600 mb-0.5">
                $1.52M →
              </div>
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-indigo-400">$2.59M</div>
              <div
                class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
              >
                Email (+70% YoY)
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
              <div class="text-base font-black text-gray-600 mb-0.5">
                $525k →
              </div>
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-indigo-400">$2.09M</div>
              <div
                class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
              >
                SMS (+298% YoY)
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-1">128.93%</div>
              <div
                class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
              >
                Retention Revenue Growth
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-1">$9.78M</div>
              <div
                class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
              >
                Total BFCM 2025 Revenue
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="col-span-2 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5"
            >
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-1">54.6%↑</div>
              <div
                class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
              >
                Total Company Revenue Growth YoY · $6.3M → $9.78M
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 italic text-center">
            Results verified via Klaviyo + SMS dashboard · BFCM 2025
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- OTAA Micro Case Study -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-0 rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-2xl shadow-emerald-500/5"
      >
        <!-- Left: story -->
        <div
          class="lg:w-[45%] bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-900 to-gray-950 p-10 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-between"
        >
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-500/15 border border-emerald-500/25 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 text-lg"
              >
                🏆
              </div>
              <span
                class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-400"
                >Black Friday · OTAA</span
              >
            </div>
            <h3
              class="font-black text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-none tracking-tight mb-4"
            >
              Busiest Week in<br />Company History.
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
              OTAA were plateauing at 15-20% Klaviyo growth. We doubled their
              revenue contribution to 40%, built out SMS flows from scratch, and
              ran their Black Friday campaign - resulting in the biggest week
              they'd ever had.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span class="text-emerald-400">✓</span> Email revenue contribution:
                21% → 40% in 90 days
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span class="text-emerald-400">✓</span> SMS flows built and launched
                from zero
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span class="text-emerald-400">✓</span> Record-breaking Black Friday
                week
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-10 text-xs text-gray-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide"
          >
            OTAA · Accessories · 8-Figure Brand · Verified
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: full testimonial + metrics -->
        <div
          class="lg:w-[55%] bg-gray-950/50 border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-white/10 p-10 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-center"
        >
          <!-- Key metrics -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
            <div
              class="col-span-2 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6"
            >
              <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-1">
                <div class="text-xl font-black text-gray-600">21%</div>
                <div class="text-gray-600">→</div>
                <div class="text-4xl font-black text-emerald-400">40%</div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide"
              >
                Email Contribution to Revenue · 90 Days
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-1">+100%</div>
              <div
                class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
              >
                Revenue Growth
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-1">$0 → Live</div>
              <div
                class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
              >
                SMS Flows Built
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Full testimonial -->
          <div
            class="rounded-2xl bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/20 p-6"
          >
            <blockquote
              class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed italic mb-5"
            >
              "Partnering with e2 agency and Jason was a pivotal moment for
              OTAA. Initially, we were plateauing at 15-20% growth on Klaviyo.
              Jason's strategic approach not only doubled our revenue growth to
              almost 40% and brought groundbreaking changes. His guidance during
              Black Friday led to the busiest week in our company's history,
              showcasing his exceptional skills in managing high-stakes
              campaigns.
              <br /><br />
              Beyond that, Jason's expertise extended to setting up SMS update flows,
              a feature we hadn't utilized before. This addition has been invaluable
              in enhancing our customer engagement and outreach. Jason's work goes
              beyond delivering solutions; he empowers teams with the knowledge and
              tools for independent growth.
              <br /><br />
              They're not just good; they're legendary."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-4">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-800 to-gray-900 border border-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 text-sm font-black flex-shrink-0"
              >
                F
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white text-sm font-bold">Fameez Haroon</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Co-Founder, OTAA</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  <!-- CTA below case studies -->

  <div class="text-center pb-16">
    <a
      href="#qualify"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-9 py-4 bg-white text-gray-950 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300 shadow-2xl"
    >
      Get Your Free Revenue Audit →
    </a>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-3">
      No obligation · We'll show you exactly what's leaking revenue right now
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
